# [作业讲解]逻辑运算符

<script>
    var score = 50;
    console.log(score >= 60);
</script>

<script>
    var year = 2001;
    //是否是闰年
    var isLeap = year % 4 === 0 && year % 100 !== 0 || year % 400 === 0;

    isLeap && console.log(29 + "天");
    isLeap || console.log(28 + "天");
</script>

<script>
    var money = 200000,
        month = 12,
        rate = 4;
    money > 100000 && (rate = rate * 1.2);
    var lixi = money * rate / 100 / 12 * month;
    console.log("利息：" + lixi);
</script>
